  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis issue here details an issue with the spec:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/issues/224\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nWe have implemented a method that doesn't underflow _or_ accept blocks until the `min_attestation_inclusion_delay`'th block.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nWe must match the spec, but the spec is wrong IMO.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nWait until this issue is resolved, then either close this issue or update our code.\r\n",
